<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَفِيهُنَا}</span> ... إِبْلِيسُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شَطَطًا}</span> ... قَوْلًا بَعِيدًا عَنِ الحَقِّ مِنْ دَعْوَى الصَّاحِبَةِ وَالوَلَدِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَعُوذُونَ}</span> ... يَسْتَجِيرُونَ، وَيَسْتَعِيذُونَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَهَقًا}</span> ... طُغْيانًا، وَسَفَهًا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَنَّهُمْ ظَنُّوا}</span> ... وَأَنَّ كُفَّارَ الإِنْسِ حَسِبُوا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَمَسْنَا السَّمَاءَ}</span> ... طَلَبْنَا بُلُوغَ السَّمَاءِ؛ لِاسْتِرَاقِ السَّمْعِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشُهُبًا}</span> ... نُجُومًا مُحْرِقَةً؛ وَذَلِكَ لَمَّا بُعِثَ النَّبِيُّ - صلى الله عليه وسلم -.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَقَاعِدَ لِلسَّمْعِ}</span> ... مَوَاضِعَ؛ لِنَسْتَمِعَ إِلَى أَخْبَارِهَا.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَّصَدًا}</span> ... أُرْصِدَ لَهُ؛ لِيُرْمَى بِهِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَشَدًا}</span> ... خَيْرًا، وَصَلَاحًا، وَرَحْمَةً.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
